Re: 仲「の」いいvs. 仲「が」いい
by coco » Mon 08.17.2009 6:38 pm Welcome to TJP forums. As NileCat-san said, 「（一番）仲の[よい/いい] 友達 」 sounds perfect. He will find it's right when he looks up the word　親友 in a dictionary.互いに信頼し合っている友達。きわめて仲のよい友達。
